des:
The SEO Drewsletter is a compilation of the latest SEO news and digital marketing trends of the week. It’s dedicated to keeping you up-to-date with the most important happenings within the digital marketing industry in a simple, easy-to-understand format. 

The SEO Drewsletter is updated every Thursday evening, so kick off your Friday morning by getting caught up on the latest digital marketing trends, SEO industry news, and Google algorithm updates.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
